    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new car smell. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in truly pristine shape, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love for you to come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
