      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute masterpiece of preservation, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains a sanctuary of pristine leather and untouched surfaces, still carrying that unmistakable new-car scent. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained with a full service history available, ensuring a driving experience that is both silent and powerful. No detail has been overlooked, from the flawless alloy wheels to the crystal-clear infotainment display. This is a rare opportunity to own a specimen in truly collector-grade condition.",
      "price": 44900.0,
