    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next home. If you're looking for total perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions.",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
