    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-quality 1997 Porsche 911 Carrera, the definitive air-cooled 993. This specimen features the M64/21 3.6L flat-six with the Varioram resonance intake system, ensuring optimal torque through the mid-range. The drivetrain is anchored by the precise G50 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Its LSA multi-link rear suspension remains factory-spec, offering unparalleled kinematic toe control. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing no signs of thermal stress. Every seal, bushing, and fastener is in concours condition. This is a turn-key investment for the serious collector demanding mechanical perfection.",
